name: Tihana, Follower of the Moon
description:
Tihana is described as a calm person, always smiling but what really characterize her is her mutism. 

Being one of the main worshipper of the lunar figure, she spend most of her time praying the moon or painting her.

Some says that her necklace is the reason of her muteness, exchanging her voice to be able to hear directly what the moon is thinking.
